      "transliteration": "Ḥattā zurtumul-maqābir(a)."
    },
    {
      "ayah": 3,
      "text": "كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ",
      "transliteration": "Kallā saufa ta‘lamūn(a)."
